<s> Hello all, In France there is at the moment a public debate on the use of electronic signature.  </s>
<s> I try to gather information on that topic and to test it with different e-mail software.  </s>
<s> Could anyone tell me what are their experience on that topic and if they know of accessibility problems with this new technology?  </s>
<s> Thank you in advance Regards Sylvie  </s>
<s> Hi Sylvie, I have come across digitally signed things from time to time using text-based systems such as pine or lynx without any digital signature software.  </s>
<s> If something requires confirmation of a signature, or requires a signature, then I would need a way of making it, but so long as the software is made properly there is no reason for it not to be accessible that I know of.  </s>
<s> cheers Charles McCN  </s>
